Heat grill. Sprinkle chicken with salt and pepper. Place chicken and sausage in grill basket. Place basket on grill. Cover and cook 15 to 20 minutes, stirring every 5 minutes, or until chicken is fork tender and juices run clear and sausage is cooked thoroughly. Meanwhile, cook pasta as directed on package. Heat pasta sauce in saucepan over medium heat. Drain pasta well and toss with sauce in large bowl; add chicken and sausage and toss again. Sprinkle with Parmesan cheese.